title: 12/13: Start or Sit (AFC); Updating the LAC-KC Running Backs (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We know you have plenty of questions about Justin Jackson and Damian Williams so we'll spend the first 5 minutes or so discussing tonight's RBs as we track the latest information. Then we've got plenty of important news items (9:03) and rankings disputes (13:13) for Deshaun Watson, Jarvis Landry and Robby Anderson ... Where we rank Jaylen Samuels at TE (23:00), discussing Josh Allen and Lamar Jackson in 4-point vs. 6-point passing TD leagues (24:00) and a great edition of Team Name Tuesday on a Thursday (25:10) ... NE-PIT (26:24), DAL-IND (36:25), CLE-DEN (42:40), OAK-CIN (46:35), TB-BAL (50:10), HOU-NYJ (56:50), DET-BUF (1:02:00), WAS-JAC (1:05:40) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
